INSTALL
=======

- Install Netbeans 7.0.1
- Install the JUnit plugin
- Install git version control plugin (tools -> plugins)


MIGRATIONS
==========

Creating a new migration:
- In the home directory, run eg.
- mvn db-migration:new -Dname=create_experiments

Bring database up to date:
- mvn db-migration:migrate

More info:
- See http://code.google.com/p/c5-db-migration/


DATABASE
========

To view the database, download and install
http://www.h2database.com/html/download.html

Database adress is: jdbc:h2:~/test
User: root
Pass: <blank>


DEPENDENCIES
============

ActiveJDBC: http://code.google.com/p/activejdbc
